snippet.title: Ship Graveyard Simulator 2 - Warships DLC | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Warships DLC is coming to Ship Graveyard Simulator 2! 🔥 Add to Wishlist and check how hard the hulls of warships are  🔨 👇
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2628300/Ship_Graveyard_Simulator_2__Warships_DLC/

Get ready for an unforgettable adventure in the world of ship demolition with the new Warships DLC! Discover the exciting world of warship demolition, where your ship demolition skills will be tested again this time with massive warships. 🚢 Wishlist Now! ⚓
